name: KFC
address: Jl. Jenderal Sudirman No.25, Karangasem, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: Very clean area, perfectly cooked chicken, and great pit stop for tourists or locals wanting a quick fix for fast food!
review 2:
One and only KFC in Town,  appreciate the comitment of the staff and owner to bring KFC to this Town.

The interior, exterior and kids facilities are good.

Well done.
review 3: Chickens are not cooked well again unfortunately. All KFC in all around the world have same peoblem I think. Because of the special crunchy sauce outside doesn't let the chicken cool well. Customer service was quite well. Thanks for kind and friendly service. It's an air-conditioned place. Seatings are quite clean. Toilets and hand wash basins are quite clean as well.
review 4: Locations in the main road, easier to find. Car and motorbikes parking available at front of the restaurant.
review 5:
Was driving on sunrise mission with my clients and then we were hungry for some great meals! Really glad we found a KFC in Karangasem.

Not only that, this place also serve with great service and nice smiles.

name: Hotel Ganitri Oka Inn
address: Subagan, Karangasem, Karangasem Regency, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: not suitable for long stay, unless you have a very tight budget. It has minimum facility but have a lot access to shops/foodstore
review 2: I stayed at this lodge on 21 Dec 2021 for one night just to sleep. Cheap room, but do not expect good  service. Even they didn't provide towels, my first experience ever. The sheet was clean n white the aircon was cool though, and that's all that matter to me

name: Wr. Babi Guling Sari Sedana
address: HJ33+2W7, Jl. Untung Surapati, Subagan, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: It was more rice than anything else. We only had two small pieces of pork. Taste was good but it doesn‚Äôt justify the 30k rupiah price. At least we had a small soup.
review 2: The Babi Guling tasted really good here. Our plates were filled with some quality piece of pig meat. Everything was juicy and tasty. We even took 2 small pieces each extra. We paid in the end 40k each with the extra meat. I think it's too much for what it is (I don't know if we paid the normal price).
review 3: Good taste, food openly displayed and flies lands on the foods, I saw big green one
review 4: local traditional food with great taste
review 5: This is a non halal restaurant. Very recommended for Balinese food lovers. One of the best restaurant around Bali. Please try if you come to this area. Come early,so you can choose the complete versions of the menu. Be careful, if you have hypertension or cholesterol problems üòÄ
